{
     "registrationId":"validRegistrationId1",
     "errorCode":200,
     "errorStatus":"Succeeded"
}

 The following JSON is an example of the result from a bulk operation.

{
    "isSuccessful":true,
    "errors": [
        {
            "registrationId":"validRegistrationId1",
            "errorCode":200,
            "errorStatus":"Succeeded"
        },
        {
            "registrationId":"validRegistrationId2",
            "errorCode":200,
            "errorStatus":"Succeeded"
        }
    ]
}

